<P>Though this &s;alt, notwith&s;tanding it is &s;ometimes given in hy|&s;teric ca&s;es, more properly belongs to the diuretic cla&s;s, as allow|ed to be a promoter of the urinary evacuation.</P>
<P>ROCK OIL&mdash;externally applied, as is al&s;o the oil of amber, in rheumatic and paralytic ca&s;es.</P>
